git submodule
-------------

adding submodule:

  git submodule add https://github.com/my-org/my-library components/my-library
  git commit -m "Add my-library as a submodule"

clone submodule:

  git clone --recurse-submodules <repository_url>     // Clone repo with it submodule
  git submodule update --init --recursive             // Update current repo with its submodule

Update submodule:

  <use your submoudle like any other repo>
  git add <submodule>                                     // Do this at your repo level
  git commit -m "Update my-library submodule to latest"

Add Git into current directory
------------------------------  

  cd /path/to/my_existing_project
  git init
  git add .
  git commit -m "Initial commit of existing local files"
  git remote add origin https://github.com/user/repo.git
  git fetch origin
  git checkout <branch>
